413
00:35:25,541 --> 00:35:27,541
E nunca mais te incomodarei.

414
00:35:30,250 --> 00:35:32,000
E sobre aquela outra coisa?

415
00:35:32,416 --> 00:35:33,708
Kelmendi?

416
00:35:34,208 --> 00:35:35,791
Dane-se Kelmendi.

417
00:35:38,250 --> 00:35:39,291
Gostou?

418
00:35:40,541 --> 00:35:42,125
Bom frango.

419
00:35:43,958 --> 00:35:45,375
De onde é?

420
00:35:46,166 --> 00:35:48,083
Do Hassan, lá da esquina.

421
00:35:52,958 --> 00:35:55,458
